{
  "stem": "142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 26,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- to do the Holocaust, always I went to young people, not to old people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it gave me some pleasure at that time with people to give them the story so they can repeat it to somebody else.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's why I do the 31 copies of the documentary to Nina.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he took them-- he took them all to-- to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to Florida, and the other people, they took it in the Midwest.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And today they're teaching that in the Midwest and Florida.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that-- that's part of my-- that I'm happy that a lot of people are doing it, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when I did that, the Sky Broadcasting told me you cannot give it to somebody.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You can't do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said fuck you, to myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 180,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I-- I did it for that purpose.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 180,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 180,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It worked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 180,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And today, you know, I gave it to too many people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 180,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Every time a family of friends, 10, 15 I will give-- see it, see it, see it, see it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 180,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- I talked to all the colleges around here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 180,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had a very good story about.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 181,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My purpose?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 181,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never ask for a penny.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 181,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Honorarium, they want to give me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 181,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, no, on this I don't want any money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 181,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I want to do it freely, like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 183,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they can-- they can know the story of the Holocaust survivors, what happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 183,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, it's more than going to see a movie or something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 183,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what the end would be.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 183,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I think it works, somehow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 183,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know, then, 20 years ago, Steven Spielberg was there.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
